How does HanumanAI work?

HanumanAI uses advanced AI technology to create content that matches your brand voice and style. Simply share your ideas through our Telegram bot, and our AI generates videos, images, blog posts, and social media content automatically. Your AI avatar can even create videos using your face and voice.

How quickly can I start creating content?

You can start generating content within minutes of approval. Most users are creating and posting content the same day they join HanumanAI.

Do I need any technical skills to use HanumanAI?

Not at all. HanumanAI is designed for non-technical users. Everything works through simple messages in Telegram - just type what you want, and get professional content instantly.

What's the application process like?

We review applications to ensure HanumanAI is a good fit for your needs. The process typically takes 24-48 hours. Once approved, you'll receive immediate access to your AI marketing team.
